INSTALLATION



********WINDOWS****************

1. Open CMD: python -m pip install pyspice
2. Navigate to this directory "C:\Users\YOUR_PC_NAME\AppData\Roaming\Python\Python39\Scripts
3. Run this command .\pyspice-post-installation --install-ngspice-dll




********LINUX****************

1. pip install pyspice
2. sudo apt update
3. sudo apt install libngspice0-dev

